{"type": "article", "id": 13438, "title": "Military HASAMI 系列单品", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-13T07:31:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002568WDj9nTzXQ6gckxe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本户外品牌  Ficouture 最近和日本陶瓷品牌 Hasami 合作，推出了 Military HASAMI 系列，他们以旅行，户外和室内三种场景作为设计核心，设计了一套陶瓷器产品。整套产品以军绿色为主，体现军事风格，霸气但又因为天然的天草陶石带来的质感不乏温润柔和。日本传统的陶瓷工艺搭配军事风格，撞击出别致的感觉。这是<a href=\"http://www.moderntimes.hk/#!ficouture/caid\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141226E4dr3pgbluyxThOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63829787\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141227rb0ePujCGHf8zI4s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63829787\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141227Hvg2alFZSBTMXID3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63829787\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141228Cl4E51zBiVtbeUXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63829787\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}